question: What is the location of the Gyeongju City Hall in Gyeongju, South Korea?
asked_question_translated: Kde sa nachádza radnica mesta Gyeongju v meste Gyeongju v Južnej Kórei?
answer: Radnica mesta Gyeongju sa nachádza v štvrti Dongcheon-dong v meste Gyeongju v Južnej Kórei.
answer_translated_eng: Gyeongju City Hall is located in the Dongcheon-dong district of Gyeongju, South Korea.
